nodes.text: A male Aqualish of the Quara race served the Confederacy of Independent Systems. However, he defected from the Confederacy later and joined the Galactic Republic. In 20 BBY, during the Clone Wars, the Aqualish served on the planet Drongar and was wounded during the battle raging on the world. He was brought to the Republic Mobile Surgical Unit 7 where he was operated on by the Duros surgeon Leemoth.
The Aqualish had a brief appearance in MedStar II: Jedi Healer, the second novel of the MedStar Duology. Jedi Healer was written by Michael Reaves and Steve Perry and published in 2004.
